			<ul>
															<li class="four-col l1">
											<h4>
							Prague:
							<a href="http://www.ivebeenthere.co.uk/tips/28829" >Carp on about Christmas</a>
						</h4>
						<p>Snowy Prague, Wenceslas Square and street corner carp vendors. We might enjoy turkey on Christmas Day but Bohemians take carp on Christmas Eve. From early&hellip;</p>
						<p class="credit">Posted by HuwJen
						<span class="date">4 Dec 2010</span>
						</p>
					</li>
															<li class="four-col edge l1">
											<h4>
							Prague:
							<a href="http://www.ivebeenthere.co.uk/tips/28827" >Leica Gallery</a>
						</h4>
						<p>We had a lovely time in this small photography gallery. The exhibition was brilliant and the cafe to the front was a great place for an early evening</p>
						<p class="credit">Posted by laura2903
						<span class="date">4 Dec 2010</span>
						</p>
					</li>
															<li class="four-col l1">
											<h4>
							Prague:
							<a href="http://www.ivebeenthere.co.uk/tips/28828" >Choco Cafe</a>
						</h4>
						<p>This gorgeous cafe came with an unexpected surprise: my hot chocolate was a cup full of smooth melted chocolate! They also do lovely pastries and have&hellip;</p>
						<p class="credit">Posted by laura2903
						<span class="date">4 Dec 2010</span>
						</p>
					</li>
															<li class="four-col edge l1">
											<h4>
							Cesky Krumlov:
							<a href="http://www.ivebeenthere.co.uk/tips/28749" >Riverside House guest apartment</a>
						</h4>
						<p>Fab self catering flat in a vaulted ground floor flat, middle of town, next to the river, access to garden which looks up at the castle tower. Full of&hellip;</p>
						<p class="credit">Posted by calgarry
						<span class="date">26 Nov 2010</span>
						</p>
					</li>
